    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a definitive example of the S54B32 high-revving architecture. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies with a linear 8,000 RPM power band. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the S54 rod bearing service and a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul have been completed. The rear subframe\u2014a critical structural point\u2014has been inspected and remains factory-perfect with no stress fractures. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M-Variable differential, ensuring optimal traction. The suspension remains taut with original geometry, and the braking system provides firm, fade-free modulation. Finished in a flawless factory coat with zero orange peel or oxidation, this M3 represents a turn-key investment for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
